9.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd371de9e9455ba2d2f713849ea957d32eee5fc","tid":364751,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:17:08.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363474\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363474</a><br />\n與此同時,LIHKG香港女神總會盃非聯賽參賽女神提名亦都已經展開,截止提名期為17年9月4日0時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf0ebd319baee33823bc6d3f5db4d21e75ef8c4","tid":364751,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e791fc6565d1cc25af03fbdab0ad06c303fffb","tid":364751,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"原來超聯有瘦苟架<br />\n上場無投到佢添<br />\n仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6c4112621200368f7ca22cebdddf1203755bc4","tid":364751,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來超聯有瘦苟架<br />\n上場無投到佢添<br />\n仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class